     H            Y.
      ** AB#RFR **********************************************
      *  FORD NOTE INQUIRY PGM                               *
      *  K.KASHIWAGI 02.16.2001                              *
JW1   *  J.WATA      2018.07.20 CHG ABFPL12 TO ABFPL21       *
JW2   *  J.WATA      2022.03.02 SET INITIAL VALUE FOR FROM/TO*
      ********************************* AB#RFR ***************
      * F3 - EXIT
      * F5 - ALL PART
      * F9 - ALL DATE
      * F12- PREVIOUS SCREEN
      ********************************* AB#RFR ***************
     FAB#PWFR CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN   KSFILE SFL01
     F**ABFPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
JW1  FABFPL21 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABFPL13 IF  E           K        DISK
     F            ABFPP201                          KRENAMEABFPPP
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     E                    MSGTBL  1   7 60
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60FDTIME
     I                                        1   20HH1
     I                                        3   40MM1
     I                                        5   60SS1
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80DATE
     I                                        1   20W@CT
     I                                        3   40W@YY
     I                                        5   60W@MM
     I                                        7   80W@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80DATE2
     I                                        1   40W@YY2
     I                                        5   60W@MM2
     I                                        7   80W@DD2
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80KDATE2
     I                                        1   40KW@YY
     I                                        5   60KW@MM
     I                                        7   80KW@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140#TIME
     I                                        1   20W@HH
     I                                        3   40W@MIN
     I                                        5   60W@SS
JW2  I                                        7  140TODAY
     I            DS
     I                                        1  60 HEAD
     I                                        1  12 FDIPAR
     I                                       13  14 STNC1
     I                                       15  180YEAR
     I                                       19  19 STNC2
     I                                       20  210MONTH
     I                                       22  22 STNC3
     I                                       23  240DAY
     I                                       25  26 STNC4
     I                                       27  280HH
     I                                       29  29 STNC5
     I                                       30  310MM
     I                                       32  32 STNC6
     I                                       33  340SS
     I                                       35  36 STNC7
     I                                       37  41 FDDOCK
     I                                       42  60 STNC8
     C*
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KDATE   60       KEY FOR DATE
     C*
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KIPAR  12        INT PART#
     C*
     C           KEY3      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KIPAR  12        INT PART#
     C                     KFLD           KDATE   60
     C*
     C           KEY5      KLIST
     C*                    KFLD           KDATE2  80
     C                     KFLD           KW@YY   40
     C                     KFLD           KW@MM   20
     C                     KFLD           KW@DD   20
     C*
     C*          *ENTRY    PLIST
     C*                    PARM           US     10
     C*
      *--------------*
      * MAIN ROUTINE *
      *--------------*
     C                     EXSR @INTR
     C           W@ID      DOWNE'99'
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'01'      @DSP1
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'02'      @DSP2
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
      *---------------*
      * INITIALIZATION
      *---------------*
     C           @INTR     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG2
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID    2
     C                     TIME           #TIME
     C                     MOVE *DATE     DATE
     C                     Z-ADD2000      W@YY4   40
     C                     ADD  W@YY      W@YY4
     C                     Z-ADD0         RRN     50
      *
JW2  C                     Z-ADDTODAY     @FMDT
 "   C                     Z-ADDTODAY     @TODT
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *--------------*
      * FIRST SCREEN *
      *--------------*
     C           @DSP1     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWFR1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG1
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN99
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN03
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN30
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN31
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN32
     C*
     C* CHK# IS USED FOR DECIDING WHICH KEY IS USED FOR READ IN
     C* SETSR
     C*
     C                     SELEC
     C           *INKA     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C*
     C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C*
     C           *INKE     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'1'       CHK#    1
     C                     EXSR CHK1SR
     C           RRN       IFGT 0
     C                     MOVEL'02'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *INKI     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'2'       CHK#
     C                     EXSR CHK2SR
     C           RRN       IFGT 0
     C                     Z-ADD0         @TODT
     C                     MOVEL'02'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     OTHER
     C                     MOVEL'3'       CHK#
     C                     EXSR CHK3SR
     C           RRN       IFGT 0
     C                     MOVEL'02'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *--------------*
      * CHK1SR*  WHEN F5 IS PRESSED
      *--------------*
     C           CHK1SR    BEGSR
     C           @IPAR     IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,2  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3099
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE @FMDT     KDATE2
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C           KEY5      CHAINAGDPL12              50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     31
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,3  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE @TODT     KDATE2
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C           KEY5      CHAINAGDPL12              50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     32
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,4  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3299
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           @FMDT     IFGT @TODT
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,5  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     313299
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     3132
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR SETSR
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
      *--------------*
      * CHK2SR* WHEN F9 IS PRESSED
      *--------------*
     C           CHK2SR    BEGSR
     C                     MOVEL@IPAR     KIPAR
     C                     SETOF                     51
     C**         KEY2      CHAINABFPL12              51
JW1  C           KEY2      CHAINABFPL21              51
     C           *IN51     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,1  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3099
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           @FMDT     IFGT 0
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,6  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     31
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           @TODT     IFGT 0
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,6  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3299
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     32
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR SETSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *--------------*
      * CHK3SR* WHEN ENTER IS PRESSED
      *--------------*
     C           CHK3SR    BEGSR
     C                     MOVEL@IPAR     KIPAR
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C**         KEY2      CHAINABFPL12              50
JW1  C           KEY2      CHAINABFPL21              50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,1  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     3099
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE @FMDT     KDATE2
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C           KEY5      CHAINAGDPL12              50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,3  @MSG1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     31
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE @TODT     KDATE2
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C           KEY5      CHAINAGDPL12              50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     3299
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,4  @MSG1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     32
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           @FMDT     IFGT 0
     C           @TODT     ANDGT0
     C           @FMDT     IFGT @TODT
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,5  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     313299
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     3132
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR SETSR
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------------*
     C* SET RECORD   THIS IS EXCUTED BEFORE GOING TO SECOND DISPLAY
     C*              SCREEN.
      *----------------------------------------------------------*
     C           SETSR     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD0         RRN              RRN FOR SFL
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   SVIPAR 12        SAVE IPAR
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   SVDOCK  5        SAVE DOCK
     C                     Z-ADD0         SVTIME  60       SAVE TIME
     C*
     C* CHK# IS USED FOR DECIDING WHICH KEY IS USED FOR READ IN
     C* SETSR
     C*
     C                     SELEC
     C           CHK#      WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE @FMDT     KDATE
     C           KEY1      SETLLABFPPP
     C*
     C           CHK#      WHEQ '2'
     C                     MOVEL@IPAR     KIPAR
     C                     Z-ADD*HIVAL    @TODT
     C**         KEY2      SETLLABFPL12
JW1  C           KEY2      SETLLABFPL21
      *
     C           CHK#      WHEQ '3'
     C                     MOVEL@IPAR     KIPAR
     C                     MOVE @FMDT     KDATE
     C**         KEY3      SETLLABFPL12
JW1  C           KEY3      SETLLABFPL21
      *
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     C                     SETOF                     51
     C           *IN51     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     SELEC
     C           CHK#      WHEQ '1'
     C                     READ ABFPPP                   51
     C           CHK#      WHEQ '2'
     C**         KEY2      READEABFPL12                  51
JW1  C           KEY2      READEABFPL21                  51
     C           CHK#      WHEQ '3'
     C**         KEY2      READEABFPL12                  51
JW1  C           KEY2      READEABFPL21                  51
     C                     ENDSL
     C*
      * 6 DIGITS YEAR TO 8 DIGITS YEAR
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD20000000  DATE2
     C                     ADD  FDDATE    DATE2
     C           *IN51     IFEQ '1'
     C           @TODT     ORLT DATE2
     C                     SETON                         51
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           SVIPAR    IFNE FDIPAR
     C           SVDOCK    ORNE FDDOCK
     C           SVTIME    ORNE FDTIME
     C                     MOVELFDDOCK    SVDOCK
     C                     MOVELFDIPAR    SVIPAR
     C                     Z-ADDFDTIME    SVTIME
     C                     Z-ADDHH1       HH
     C                     Z-ADDMM1       MM
     C                     Z-ADDSS1       SS
     C                     Z-ADD20000000  DATE2
     C                     ADD  FDDATE    DATE2
     C                     MOVE W@YY2     YEAR
     C                     MOVEL'/'       STNC2
     C                     MOVEL'/'       STNC3
     C                     MOVEL':'       STNC5
     C                     MOVEL':'       STNC6
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   STNC1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   STNC4
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   STNC7
     C                     MOVE W@MM2     MONTH
     C                     MOVE W@DD2     DAY
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         RRN
     C                     SETON                     65
     C                     MOVELHEAD      @NOTE
     C                     WRITESFL01
     C                     SETOF                     65
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         RRN
     C                     MOVELFDNOTE    @NOTE
     C                     WRITESFL01
     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETOF                     55
     C                     ADD  1         RRN
     C                     MOVELFDNOTE    @NOTE
     C                     WRITESFL01
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C           RRN       IFEQ 0
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,7  @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
      *---------------*
      * SECOND SCREEN *
      *---------------*
     C           @DSP2     BEGSR
     C                     WRITEFMT90
     C                     MOVEL'1'       *IN70
     C                     EXFMTSFLCTL
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG2
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN99
     C                     MOVEL'0'       *IN70
     C*
     C                     SELEC
     C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C           *INKL     WHEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR @CLRSR
     C                     Z-ADD0         RRN
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C                     ENDSL
     C                     ENDSR
     C****************
     C* CLEAR SFL
     C****************
     C           @CLRSR    BEGSR
     C                     SETON                     71
     C                     WRITESFLCTL
     C                     SETOF                     71
     C                     Z-ADD0         RRN
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFR1
     C                     ENDSR
** (MSGTBL)
E-01 INVALID PART NUMBER.
E-02 PART NUMBER SHOULD BE BLANK.
E-03 INVALID FROM DATE.
E-04 INVALID TO DATE.
E-05 FROM DATE SHOULD NOT BE GREATER THAN TO DATE.
E-06 DATE SHOULD BE 0.
E-07 THERE IS NO MATCHED RECORD.
